 <body>
  <section name="New Releases">
   <p>May 31, 2011.  The OpenIDM team has announced OpenIDM 2.0 
   Milestone 1, the revolutionary step towards the next generation, 
   lightweight, scalable, highly modular and developer friendly 
   Identity Management solution.  OpenIDM 2.0 Milestone 1 includes 
   full capability to perform synchronization, reconciliation and 
   basic account administration as well as exposing a RESTful web 
   API to the core services of OpenIDM. Visit the 
   <a href="http://openidm.forgerock.org/downloads.html">download page</a> 
   to get started.
  </p>
